dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.corecommunication

Interface IISignalTriggering

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IISignalTriggering
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IISignalTriggering: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A ISignalTriggering defines the manner of triggering of a ISignal on the channel, on which it is sent. ISignalTriggering should only be used for defining timing constraints. Com does not know of signals related to a specific cluster or channel.
